  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Enhancing Uganda&apos;s Border Managament Information System</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project supports the integration of the Border Management Information Systems in Uganda, specifically the connectivity of the INTERPOL I-24/7, the IOM MIDAS-Migration Information and Data Analysis System, the PISCES-Personal Identification Secure Comparison and Evaluation System and the Gemalto Self |Service Kiosks. The integration of these systems will further promote realtime cooperation, interdictions, information sharing between neigbouring states and is key to improve overall border management.</narrative>
  </description>
